                      "subject": "Fullfilment Altruista Metadata file Load Failed",
                      "body": "Fullfilment Altruista Metadata file Load process can not run while there is another process listed on the P_RUN_CYC as running.\n\nSource    =  ALTRUISTA HEALTH\n\nTarget    = COMM TRNSMSN Database ( Fullfilment Broker)\n\nSubject   = Fullfillment\n\nFrequency = Every 30 Minutes",
